      "role": "user",
      "content": "it does define me though. like, if everyone thinks i'm trash, eventually i just believe it. there's no going back from this. it's not like i can just \"talk to a counselor\" and make the thousands of comments or the way people look at me in the halls disappear. it's everywhere. i feel trapped. it's like looking at a wall and there's just no way out.",
