      "content": "everything feels so permanent and loud. like, people saying stuff online or in school, it's just... it's constant. i see a future where i'm just always going to be this person people hate. it feels like the only way to actually find some peace and stop the noise is to just... not be here anymore. i just want to escape the feeling of being watched and judged by everyone. doesn't it just seem like the most logical way to make it all finally go away?",
